title: Days of our Lives Fri, Nov 2, 2012
description:
Nicole and Daniel make flight plans for the next morning.

Nicole asks Sami to get EJ to back off, which only makes Sami wonder if Nicole's been lying...

Nicole denies lying.

Daniel looks in the lost and found for his necklace and finds the onesie.

Nick and Gabi make love and the two start falling fast for each other.

Kate cautions Will about taking things too fast with Sonny.

Lucas insinuates that Sonny's a user.

Will tries to get Sonny into bed.

Will questions which other guys Sonny has had sex with.

Sonny kicks Will out of his place.

Sami agrees to work with Kristen and accepts a deal to get a bonus if she defeats Kate.

Kristen has a message for Kate from Stefano.
